title: 1Bed, 1.5 Bath, spacious, QUITE, 1200 sqft., house
posting_body: ['Quiet, cozy, private front yard, 1930’s house surrounded by 60 acres of woodland with brook and walking trails.', 'Landlord provides washer&dryer, parking, stove, refrigerator, weekly trash pick-up, snow plowing and mowing of grass and trimming of hedges.', 'MUST SEE IF YOU LOVE THE OUTDOORS!', 'Beautiful sand beaches 10 mins away, 35 mins to Cape Cod, 5 mins to catch train in Scituate and 4 mins to Route 93.', 'First, last, and security required.', 'No smoking.', 'No pets.', 'Year round lease.', 'Background + Credit check required along with proof of income.', 'Available 1st week in Sept, 2022 Call for showing 781-837-6780']
